request.description:
Get available credit packages for purchase

Returns:
    List of available credit packages with pricing

Example response:
{
    "packages": [
        {
            "id": "starter",
            "name": "Starter Pack",
            "credits": 1000,
            "amount": 1000,
            "currency": "usd",
            "description": "Perfect for trying out the platform"
        }
    ]
}
